com.itranswarp.jsonstream

Interface TypeAdapter<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type to serialize or deserialize to.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DateTimeTypeAdapter, DateTypeAdapter, TimeTypeAdapter

    public interface TypeAdapter<T>
    Register a type adapter to convert between this type and string. TypeAdapter are only used to serialize or deserialize a JavaBean.
    Author:
    Michael Liao
